Class PieceIterator

  • java.lang.Object
    • VASSAL.counters.PieceIterator

  • public class PieceIterator
extends java.lang.Object
    An iterator for GamePieces. Takes an optional PieceFilter to extract GamePiece instances from an Enumeration or Iterator.
